{"id":441742,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":3,"day":29}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"167","ytitle":"","mtitle":"棍和鞭","ftitle":"","authors":["郑成义"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑成义　配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志:请张开你的眼睛——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是美帝特制专打华工的皮包铅棍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是专打学徒的藤条、戒尺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是“打死不论”的护法盘龙棍……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棍一淌血呵!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一鞭半寸深；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少阶级兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在棍鞭下丧生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别认为它们已经躺在橱窗里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一有机会，它们都想复生；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要牢牢记住雷锋的话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“夺过鞭子揍敌人。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1963\\03\\633t020901.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>反动派的棍和鞭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海工人文化宫举办“阶级教育展览会”展品</FONT>"}]}